title: Elisha Cuthbert Returns
itunes:title: Elisha Cuthbert Returns
description:
Elisha Cuthbert [24, The Girl Next Door, Happy Endings, The Ranch, The Cellar] talks with Anna about having kids, the blind date that led to the kids, being married to an athlete, getting in to comedies, horror-film screams, learning from past relationships, dealbreakers and much more!


First on this episode’s Unqualified segment is Anjelica, whose friend and co-worker is weighing down the workplace with her constant negativity. Anjelica wonders if there’s a way to help so her friend doesn’t lose her job.


Next is Simone who, after a surprise break-up, is having a hard time moving on from her ex when he keeps texting her.


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
